//--- SILAS description -----------------------------------------------------

/**
@mainpage SILAS Developer Documentation

The simulator for large scale applications SILAS provides an
infrastructure to model and simulate the application behaviour of large
scale applications based on event traces.

The simulator can be devided in three main modules:
    * the simulation infrastructure,
    * the simulation model, and
    * the hypotheses with their implied transformations.

The entire functionality is encapsulated in the namespace @ref silas.
*/


